sp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;">Hở socket gắn CPU (do họat động l&acirc;u ng&agrave;y v&agrave; nhiệt độ cao)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 13.5pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;">4.<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;">Lỗi chip BIOS ROM (th&aacute;o ch&iacute;p BIOS ROM ra vệ sinh, nếu kh&ocirc;ng th&igrave; nạp lại thử)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 13.5pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;">5.<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;">Hở ch&iacute;p cầu Bắc (phải hấp chip hoặc đ&oacute;ng lại chip, c&aacute;i n&agrave;y phải c&oacute; m&aacute;y đ&oacute;ng chip mới l&agrave;m được)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 13.5pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; fon